// Page FirstVisit Text :
"P707189285" "You've heard some stuff on the street."
// Answer Text :
"P4060782435" "Leave"
// Page HelloPage Text :
"P325879497" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>My Other Selves</color></span></scale></font><br><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Villain Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You find an odd circle with a small button on it. Upon pressing the button, a small holographic image springs to life - and it's an image of you!<br><br>'{HeroName}, listen to me.  I am you from many years in the future. I have spent nearly all of my incalculable power to send this message back in time so that you can correct the one critical flaw that I - you - made in my - our - master plan'.<br><br>Deep down inside, you know that the person you're seeing might truly... be you.  And if it is - and in the future you can span time and space - then you MUST know what that mistake is... and see to it that you never make it!<br><br><color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your alignment to Villain. Becoming a Villain means you will be unable to travel to Paragon City. Any ties to a heroic world will be lost.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1891803962" "Learn where your master plan went wrong...and fix it!"
// Page ImVillain Text :
"P3182786706" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will maintain your current alignment of Villain, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignments.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2645858695" "On second thought, I'll hold off on this at the moment."
// Page ImVigilante Text :
"P2467728045" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your current alignment of Vigilante to Villain, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignment. Becoming a Villain means you will no longer be able to travel to Paragon City. It will sever all ties with the Hero world.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2055348475" "Yes, I want to learn where my master plan went wrong...and fix it!"
// Page ImRogue Text :
"P2444490737" "<color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your current alignment of Rogue to Villain, removing any progress you may have made on any other alignment. Becoming a Villain again means you will no longer be able to travel to Paragon City. It will sever all ties with the Hero world.<br><br>Are you sure you want to do this?</color>"
