// Page FirstVisit Text :
// Answer Text :
// Page HelloPage Text :
"P972823489" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Hometown Hero</color></span></scale></font><br><br><span align=center><color orange><i>Villain Morality Mission</i></color></span><br><br>While going about your business, you find a news article from the Paragon Times concerning you. You read it over to see that it's an interesting interview with Desdemona...<br><br><scale 1.1><font face=computer><color BurlyWood>Yes, I would like to say something about {HeroName}. If you're reading this, {HeroName}, know that I will <i>not</i> tolerate all of your vile actions in the Rogue Isles. As of today, I have decided that I will make it my personal goal to ensure that you are brought to true <i>justice</i> for all your heinous actions. I will not rest until the world knows it is safe from you and anyone like you!</color></font></scale><br><br>It looks like Desdemona's days as a villain are far behind her, enough that she's forgotten what happens when you try to <i>threaten</i> someone such as yourself. You do a little digging to find that Desdemona has made a little home for herself in Croatoa. It would just be <i>terrible</i> if something <i>bad</i> were to happen in Croatoa because of what she said in that news article...<br><br><color orange>WARNING: This is a Morality Mission. Completing this mission will change your alignment to Villain. Becoming a Villain means you will be unable to travel to Paragon City. Any ties to a heroic world will be lost.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P131795896" "Burn part of Croatoa to show Desdemona her mistake!"
// Page ImVillain Text :
// Answer Text :
// Page ImVigilante Text :
// Answer Text :
"P2548538516" "Yes, I'll burn down part of Croatoa to show Desdemona her mistake!"
// Page ImRogue Text :
